title:

creator: G5 Entertainment
descriptionHtml:
Solve puzzles and riddles in a free hidden object mobile adventure game!



You are a member of The Secret Society® - a clandestine community of people with the unique ability to move through magical worlds, find hidden items & treasures and play mystery puzzles. Your uncle's gone missing and you arrive at his manor in search for clues that will lead to solving the mystery of his sudden disappearance. Who's responsible for this crime? What secrets are hidden in the dark corridors of this mansion?



There are many ways of hunting for clues in our mystery game: search for hidden items, collect pieces of photographs, solve logical puzzles, find the differences between pictures and even solving match-3 puzzles!



  • Explore the manor and solve its mysteries

  • You are free to play different game modes at your own pace: from finding objects to solving unique puzzles

  • Search for items & clues that will help you to solve your uncle's mystery

  • Get free game bonuses every day!



    • Seek and piece together notes to solve great enigmas of your uncle's mansion full of mystery. Immerse yourself in a mysterious story with unexpected plot twists while you explore free finding object game worlds full of enchanting characters. Swap and match gems in an ingenious puzzle wrapped in a finding objects mystery game for free. Enjoy updates with additional quests to find clues and continue your own journey in search for clues and useful items that will aid you on your quest.




    Go on a mystery adventure, find hidden objects, combine items into collections and complete quests to protect the sacred Artifact of the Order and thwart the forces threatening the entire society in this fantastic world of hidden object pictures and puzzles!



    While The Secret Society® - Hidden Objects Mystery Game is absolutely free to play, you have the ability to unlock optional bonuses via in-app purchases from within the game. You may disable in-app purchases in your device settings.



    You can play this game both offline or online.
